
DrawableObject
	- Polygon
	+ draw(Point coordinate)

AnimationPath
	- List of Points
	- Reference to the current Point
	- List of DrawableObject's

Model
	- List of DrawableObjects
	- List of AnimationPaths
	+ addObject(DrawableObject obj)
	+ eraseObject(DrawableObject obj)
	+ addPath(AnimationPath path)
	+ erasePath(AnimationPath path)

Mode (Interface implements MouseAdapter)
	+ mousePressed
	+ mouseDragged
